creator: Julia Caroline Dorr
description:
LibriVox recording of Afternoon Songs by Julia Caroline Dorr.
Read in English by Domenica Campbell; Sarah Sellari; Jael Baldwin; GregShinn; SkyAlbatross; Rachel; Ezwa; Larry Wilson; Michele Fry; Lana Maes; dane hendren; Newgatenovelist; Diana Schmidt
This is a volume of poems by Julia Caroline Dorr, part 5 of her collected poems. - Summary by Carolin
